services.name: ProtocolService
services.description:
ProtocolService is the top-level API to manage an instance of the Berty Protocol.
Each Berty Protocol Instance is considered as a Berty device and is associated with a Berty user.

methods.name: InstanceExportData
methods.description: InstanceExportData exports instance data

methods.description: ContactRequestSend attempt to send a contact request

methods.description: ContactAliasKeySend send an alias key to a contact, the contact will be able to assert that your account is being present on a multi-member group
